## UI Feature Flags

### showAdvanced (React State)
**Type**: boolean state variable
**Default**: false
**Purpose**: Toggle visibility of advanced workout options (duration, intensity, focus, equipment)
**Implementation**: Controlled by chevron button in workout builder
